description:
Uh oh!  Dot is drifting toward an asteroid field.  One "big bang" with these big rocks and Dot will be space dust!  
Help Dot use the engines to avoid the asteroids!

puzzles.description: Make Dot automatically play the jet sound. Then make Dot wait for 1.0 s and do nothing.

hints.description: Link Start to the Jet sound using an Auto cue. Link the sound to the Do Nothing state using a Wait For cue set to 1.0 s.

puzzles.description: After doing nothing, make Dot wait for a random time up to 2.0 s then play a warning sound. Then make Dot wait for 1.0 s and turn on red lights.

hints.description: Choose a warning sound. Link the Do Nothing state to the sound using a Random Wait cue set to 2.0 s. Link the sound to the Red light using a Wait For cue set to 1.0 s.

puzzles.description: After turning on red lights, make Dot randomly choose a direction sound. Make Dot choose between left, right, up, or down.

hints.description: Link the states with Random Link cues.

puzzles.description: After each direction sound, make Dot wait for 2.0 s then play the siren sound. Then make Dot wait for 1.0 s and play the short rocket boost sound.

hints.description: Link each direction sound to the Siren sound using Wait For cues set to 2.0 s. Link the Siren sound to the Short rocket boost sound using a Wait For cue set to 1.0 s.

puzzles.description: After the Short rocket boost sound, make Dot instantly turn the lights off then automatically turn off all eye lights.

hints.description: Link the Short rocket boost sound to the Lights Off state using an Instant cue. Link the light to the Eye Ring using an Auto cue.

puzzles.description: After turning off the eye lights, make Dot automatically play the Dizzy #1 sound. Then make Dot return to Start when the top button is pressed.
puzzles.introduction: Uh oh! Dot had a crash! Let's use the top button to reset the spaceship.

hints.description: Link the Eye Ring to the Dizzy #1 sound using an Auto cue. Link the Dizzy #1 sound to Start using a Top Button Pressed cue.

puzzles.description: After Dot says each direction, make Dot turn on cyan lights when tilted in the correct direction to match the sound.

hints.description: Link the sounds to the Cyan light using the correct cue. Use a Lean Left cue for "Left", Lean Right cue for "Right", a Face Up cue for "Up", and a Face Down cue for "Down".

puzzles.description: After turning on cyan lights, make Dot automatically play the jet sound again.
puzzles.introduction: Stay sharp!  For each asteroid you avoid, there's another one headed your way!

hints.description: Link the states with an Auto cue.

puzzles.description: PLAY WITH DOT: Help Dot fly through space and avoid three asteroids.
puzzles.introduction: Time to rock it! Let's see how well you can help Dot avoid the asteroids!
